Nifty Tours traveling agency has a target market of both male and female with no age or marital status restriction. Nifty Tours customer has at least 2 years of college education and makes upwards of $60,000 a year. Customers have interests in travel in single or as group, culture, and history. Majority of Nifty's Tours customers are from United States and Canada but there are some from other countries where services are offered.
